Note on primary sources:

This archive does NOT host the underlying primary-source documents
themselves. Those are public records produced by the Iowa City Community
School District and remain on the district's Simbli eBoardSolutions site at
https://simbli.eboardsolutions.com/. Each meeting page in this archive links
back to the originals. Re-use of those primary-source PDFs is governed by
public-records law, not by this license.
